        <summary>Door won't close flush</summary>
        <p>Hinge wear. Doors weigh 35-120 lb depending on config. Pair replacement recommended $360-$520 (single $195-$285). VDOF French-door has different hinge ($285-$425 assembly). Gasket often needs simultaneous replacement.</p>
      </details>

      <details class="faq">
        <summary>Premiere vs Select vs French-door?</summary>
        <p>Same core convection and heating architecture. Premiere = flagship with 11 modes, Gourmet-Glo broiler, TruGlide racks. Select = fewer features. VDOF French-door = side-opening doors essential where island spacing is &lt;48". Most service parts shared across tiers.</p>
      </details>

      <details class="faq">
        <summary>Combi-steam oven (MVSOC) maintenance</summary>
        <p>Descaling every 8-12 months LA water (200-350 ppm). $185 flat descaling service. Neglected = element failure $345-$485. Preventive cheaper than reactive.</p>
      </details>

      <details class="faq">
        <summary>How much does Viking wall oven repair cost?</summary>
        <p>Diagnostic $89, waived with repair. Common: bake element $265-$385, convection fan $385-$540, RTD probe $165-$245, thermal fuse $135-$195, door hinge pair $360-$520, control board $680-$940. Full pricing above.</p>
      </details>
    </div>
